If request header Accept includes "text/markdown" for a public HTML page:
  return status 200
  set Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=utf-8
  set Vary: Accept
  return a concise Markdown representation of the same canonical page URL

Otherwise:
  continue to the normal HTML route

Never apply markdown negotiation to:
  /api/*
  /_next/*
  /assets/*
  /robots.txt
  /sitemap.xml
  /llms.txt
  /AGENTS.md
  /.well-known/*
